  "recipe_notes": [
    "Traditional binatog uses dried mature white corn soaked in water and lye until puffed. Canned hominy is a convenient shortcut that eliminates the soaking process."
  ],
  "storage_notes": [
    "Refrigerate leftovers in an airtight container for up to 2 days. Best served fresh as the coconut may dry out."
